Title: Columbia River Reservoir Clear. Proj.; CAPTION: CAMP DETILLION, LIIKING (sic) EAST (May 15).Camp Detillion a small clearing camp during the final days of clearing operations in this area is seen in this view looking east. The cleared Spokane river valley is seen in the background. Reservoir lake water will eventually cover the site of this clearing.

PH Coll 478.289
